<div class="flex items-center justify-center" style="height: 80vh;">
  <div class="flex gap-4 overflow-auto max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
    <div class="relative max-w-xs w-full border border-solid border-gray-200 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden bg-white">
      <div class="block overflow-hidden">
        <img src="<%= image_path('入力フォーム.png') %>" alt="Card image" class="max-h-48 object-contain" />
      </div>
      <div class="p-4">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 capitalize transition-all duration-500">単語登録</h4>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500 transition-all duration-500 leading-5 mb-8">指文字に変換したいひらがなを登録することができます</p>
        <%= link_to '登録', new_hiragana_path, class: "bg-indigo-600 shadow-sm rounded-full py-2 px-5 text-xs text-white font-semibold" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-xs w-full border border-solid border-gray-200 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden bg-white">
      <div class="block overflow-hidden">
        <img src="<%= image_path('一覧・再生.png') %>" alt="Card image" class="max-h-48 object-contain" />
      </div>
      <div class="p-4">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 capitalize transition-all duration-500">一覧・再生</h4>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500 transition-all duration-500 leading-5 mb-8">登録したひらがなの一覧を確認し、指文字を再生できます。</p>
        <%= link_to '確認', hiraganas_path, class: "bg-indigo-600 shadow-sm rounded-full py-2 px-5 text-xs text-white font-semibold" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-xs w-full border border-solid border-gray-200 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 overflow-hidden bg-white">
      <div class="block overflow-hidden">
        <img src="<%= image_path('一覧・再生.png') %>" alt="Card image" class="max-h-48 object-contain" />
      </div>
      <div class="p-4">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 capitalize transition-all duration-500">学習</h4>
        <p class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500 transition-all duration-500 leading-5 mb-8">登録した単語学習することができます。</p>
        <% if @hiragana %>
          <%= link_to '学習', study_hiragana_path(@hiragana), class: "bg-indigo-600 shadow-sm rounded-full py-2 px-5 text-xs text-white font-semibold", data: { turbo: false} %>
        <% else %>
          <p>学習するひらがなが登録されていません。</p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
